{"tid":2125114,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"機場行李運送員工初步確診","createTime":"2020-07-26T03:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T03:37:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3499c6456745b4032ee6bcf38dc3466936dd8775","tid":2125114,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:13:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539912-20200726.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539912-20200726.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=94e898cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539912-20200726.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bbb94678\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539912-20200726.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n機管局昨日收到通知，一名行李運送系統工程承辦商員工初步確診新型肺炎。據了解，該員工早前因身體不適申請一星期病假，最後上班日期為 7 月 18 日。機管局說，他曾使用的辦公室、工地範圍，以及禁區地庫行李處理大堂將進行消毒及清潔。<br />\n<br />\n機管局說已安排曾與該名員工接觸的大約十多名機管局職員接受檢測，並在等候檢測結果期間在家工作。該工程亦會暫時停止直至 7 月 28 日。"},{"pid":"aaa135b4cf2cb94f19091a73fe31ac9970fbbbb3","tid":2125114,"uid":106,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"全港大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8a57f9b61818b37351fa65a313f3e2ded9bb91","tid":2125114,"uid":312363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:14:46.000Z","msg":"BOOMMMM"},{"pid":"3fe90d4a07f6a4a0e56c38ef7043c85f7d23b7a6","tid":2125114,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"冇事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b3744207a895fea5a0d0e442e2a826492be910","tid":2125114,"uid":212702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:15:58.000Z","msg":"高危行業"},{"pid":"47f115e4b546515ac75117e60a431438f909c